title: Live Oak Unified School District

creator: CatapultK12
descriptionHtml:
The new Live Oak Unified School District app provides the core information parents and families need to keep up to date with school and district matters.

The app includes information for the district and all schools. Filter by the school your child attends to feature information for that school.

Key information includes:
• Announcements
• Contact Details
• Staff Directory
• Event Calendar

Additional resources may be provided by the district or school such as:
• bus routes
• board agendas
• lunch menus
• Aeries & MySchoolBucks login links
• sports information
• and more

App users may opt to receive push notifications with important alerts from the district.
descriptionShort: Live Oak USD Parent App keeps parents up to date.
